{"tid":1544931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南區終於有嘢搞","createTime":"2019-09-05T17:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T04:38:36.000Z","uid":232728,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"60ebef563f93ada59dc979c8aaea93eea7079d7f","tid":1544931,"uid":232728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:23:44.000Z","msg":"雖然唔係咩遊行集會，但都希望比多啲人知呢件事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G1v8z8r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1v8z8r.jpg&h=680cb278&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月6號 夜晚8點 海濱見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n另外，繼前幾日培德同聖伯多祿仲有聖心有人鏈，聽日(9月6)幾間南區中學都會有人鏈。係呢到講聲對唔住，有啲遲出po。<br />\n<br />\n其中聖伯多祿再次出手<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/372bxVq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F372bxVq.jpg&h=8c85d53c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後，利東浸信會呂明才都會有人鏈<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4CZ1U9n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4CZ1U9n.jpg&h=c0e52daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後就係華富之路：聖呂、明莊、培英合力整條華富之路出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JPhbxWR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJPhbxWR.jpg&h=0df286a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望咁多位南區人去番自己母校幫幫手喇<br />\n再次係到講聲對唔住，太遲先出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過利申番先：唔係任何一個活動嘅搞手"},{"pid":"d3f510e81c3e3a65757214505f7cc9f6cb072bcf","tid":1544931,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:23:59.000Z","msg":"[行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/reLz9Yb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FreLz9Yb.jpg&h=bc5ea362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VeJJ3id